223
00:13:36,100 --> 00:13:37,990
Later, people thought of

224
00:13:38,660 --> 00:13:41,510
marking the emerald jades when they stumbled upon them.

225
00:13:41,510 --> 00:13:43,660
This way, if the locals see it,

226
00:13:43,730 --> 00:13:45,100
they will avoid it.

227
00:13:47,130 --> 00:13:49,130
