Suhua's body?

285
00:16:25,390 --> 00:16:29,790
There is a deep cave at the foot of the mountain.

286
00:16:30,220 --> 00:16:31,720
It rained heavily a few days ago

287
00:16:31,720 --> 00:16:33,400
and several bodies were washed out.

288
00:16:33,400 --> 00:16:36,640
They were all the bodies of the girls abducted by the King of Hell.

289
00:16:36,640 --> 00:16:39,530
I recognized Suhua at first sight.

290
00:16:44,880 --> 00:16:46,120
Where are the bodies

291
00:16:46,890 --> 00:16:48,000
of the other girls?

292
00:16:48,630 --> 00:16:51,240
The families are afraid to claim the bodies

293
00:16:52,270 --> 00:16:54,090
of the girls abducted by the King of Hell.

294
00:16:54,090 --> 00:16:56,460
They are in the morgue.

295
00:17:06,130 --> 00:17:11,710
[Promote friendly relations]

296
00:17:08,040 --> 00:17:12,020
From A1 to B7 in the east of the city,

297
00:17:12,540 --> 00:17:16,099
and from C4 to D3 in the south of the city.

298
00:17:16,609 --> 00:17:17,290
Young Master,

299
00:17:17,290 --> 00:17:19,099
we've almost searched the entire Xiaoyuan City.

300
00:17:19,099 --> 00:17:22,500
But we still don't have any clues about Madam's whereabouts.

301
00:17:23,130 --> 00:17:23,930
Young Master.

302
00:17:24,990 --> 00:17:26,319
What are you looking at?

303
00:17:26,900 --> 00:17:28,359
Why is there a river pebble

304
00:17:28,660 --> 00:17:30,140
in the mine?

305
00:17:32,040 --> 00:17:32,520
Li,

306
00:17:32,849 --> 00:17:33,420
ask the government

307
00:17:33,420 --> 00:17:35,090
for Xiaoyuan City's ore record.

308
00:17:35,090 --> 00:17:36,220
Ore record?

309
00:17:36,850 --> 00:17:37,250
Okay.

310
00:17:42,720 --> 00:17:49,130
[Morgue]

311
00:18:13,670 --> 00:18:14,270
Pardon me.

312
00:18:31,660 --> 00:18:33,220
These victims indeed have

313
00:18:33,890 --> 00:18:36,340
the poison palm left over by Yunuqiao.

314
00:18:38,340 --> 00:18:41,940
Maybe it's because of this palm that the bodies haven't decayed.

315
00:18:42,460 --> 00:18:42,920
Bashi.

316
00:18:43,730 --> 00:18:46,190
Why did you say that the culprit was not the King of Hell,

317
00:18:46,190 --> 00:18:47,050
but a criminal?

318
00:18:47,100 --> 00:18:48,780
If... If he really were the King of Hell,

319
00:18:48,780 --> 00:18:50,980
why did he only appear in Xiaoyuan City?

320
00:18:51,310 --> 00:18:53,860
If the girl escapes from the city, she'll be safe.

321
00:18:53,860 --> 00:18:54,730
You're right.

322
00:18:55,310 --> 00:18:56,380
I guess this person

323
00:18:56,660 --> 00:18:58,530
used the mines to sneak out.

324
00:18:59,140 --> 00:19:00,550
Do the underground mines

325
00:19:00,970 --> 00:19:02,690
connect to the entire city?

326
00:19:02,860 --> 00:19:05,340
More than half of the houses are connected to the mines.

327
00:19:05,340 --> 00:19:09,240
But the underground mines are full of twists and turns.

328
00:19:09,410 --> 00:19:10,370
I don't know

329
00:19:10,400 --> 00:19:12,320
where they all lead to.

330
00:19:12,540 --> 00:19:14,340
It's so complicated down there,

331
00:19:14,660 --> 00:19:17,190
but he was able to find where these girls were.

332
00:19:18,190 --> 00:19:19,690
How did the King of Hell

333
00:19:19,710 --> 00:19:21,100
choose his victims,

334
00:19:22,070 --> 00:19:22,800
and how did he

335
00:19:22,820 --> 00:19:24,880
find their locations so accurately?

336
00:19:26,830 --> 00:19:27,390
Bashi.

337
00:19:28,470 --> 00:19:29,470
Did these girls

338
00:19:29,820 --> 00:19:31,220
have anything in common?

339
00:19:31,490 --> 00:19:32,650
Did they live in the same area?

340
00:19:32,650 --> 00:19:34,240
No.

341
00:19:34,400 --> 00:19:36,730
They were scattered throughout the city.

342
00:19:38,190 --> 00:19:40,050
Did they have any common friends,

343
00:19:40,110 --> 00:19:42,800
or did their families practice the same trade?

344
00:19:43,250 --> 00:19:45,780
Their families practiced different trades.

345
00:19:45,900 --> 00:19:48,220
As for common friends,

346
00:19:48,540 --> 00:19:49,900
I'm not sure.

347
00:19:49,900 --> 00:19:51,560
After all, this city is small.

348
00:19:51,730 --> 00:19:53,190
Everyone knows everyone.

349
00:19:55,660 --> 00:19:57,980
They don't seem to be related on the surface.

350
00:19:57,980 --> 00:19:59,750
But there must be a connection.

351
00:20:01,250 --> 00:20:03,980
The King of Hell has never failed in an operation.

352
00:20:04,660 --> 00:20:07,060
Even if he can travel freely under the mine,

353
00:20:07,540 --> 00:20:08,460
how did he know

354
00:20:08,460 --> 00:20:10,220
which room every girl lived in?

355
00:20:11,400 --> 00:20:13,600
He must have entered the houses before.

356
00:20:20,100 --> 00:20:20,900
Acupuncture.

357
00:20:25,450 --> 00:20:26,450
Cupping therapy.

358
00:20:34,540 --> 00:20:35,100
Bashi.

359
00:20:36,480 --> 00:20:38,970
Did Suhua see a physician before she died?

360
00:20:41,020 --> 00:20:44,290
That day, S-Suhua's mother had a headache.

361
00:20:44,560 --> 00:20:46,640
She did call a physician.

362
00:20:50,980 --> 00:20:51,500
Madam.

363
00:20:51,500 --> 00:20:53,360
The physician sent the medicine.

364
00:20:53,610 --> 00:20:54,320
That's it.

365
00:20:55,220 --> 00:20:58,050
The identity of a physician is safe and reasonable.

366
00:20:58,050 --> 00:21:00,570
He can enter a lady's house to visit her

367
00:21:01,570 --> 00:21:03,230
without arousing suspicion.

368
00:21:08,360 --> 00:21:12,140
[Xiaoyuan City]

369
00:21:14,040 --> 00:21:17,140
[Mysterious Lotus Casebook]

370
00:21:20,990 --> 00:21:21,710
[Ore Record]

371
00:21:27,180 --> 00:21:30,110
Xiaoyuan City doesn't produce white river pebbles.

372
00:21:30,380 --> 00:21:32,910
It's only found in the west, outside the city.

373
00:21:33,460 --> 00:21:34,540
Did someone

374
00:21:34,890 --> 00:21:36,550
drop it in the well on purpose?

375
00:21:38,080 --> 00:21:38,480
Li,

376
00:21:44,060 --> 00:21:45,660
have you seen any outsiders

377
00:21:45,660 --> 00:21:47,260
in and out of Baishui Garden?

378
00:21:47,700 --> 00:21:48,700
There were plenty of them.

379
00:21:48,700 --> 00:21:49,890
We hired many craftsmen

380
00:21:49,890 --> 00:21:51,550
for the renovation of the old garden.

381
00:21:51,550 --> 00:21:53,880
Was there any craftsman near the dry well?

382
00:21:55,350 --> 00:21:56,060
It's a remote place.

383
00:21:56,060 --> 00:21:57,320
Few people went there.

384
00:22:00,470 --> 00:22:01,200
What is this?

385
00:22:02,270 --> 00:22:03,740
Didn't Madam have diarrhea before?

386
00:22:03,740 --> 00:22:04,830
The physician prescribed some medicine.

387
00:22:04,830 --> 00:22:05,960
This is the residue.

388
00:22:14,280 --> 00:22:15,940
This was for diarrhea, right?

389
00:22:16,180 --> 00:22:18,320
Then why does it have xijiang grass, which is used to cure poisoning?

390
00:22:18,320 --> 00:22:20,450
It's hard for ordinary people to tell.

391
00:22:20,720 --> 00:22:22,220
If it weren't for people like us

392
00:22:22,220 --> 00:22:24,140
who have been miners for decades,

393
00:22:24,350 --> 00:22:25,950
who can tell the difference?

394
00:22:26,630 --> 00:22:28,020
Where was the physician mixing the herbs?

395
00:22:28,020 --> 00:22:29,880
In the side hall near the dry well.

396
00:22:31,780 --> 00:22:32,460
It's him.

397
00:22:32,880 --> 00:22:33,810
What do you mean?

398
00:22:34,060 --> 00:22:36,300
Not many people know about the emerald jade's poison.

399
00:22:36,300 --> 00:22:38,700
But he prescribed the antidote right away.

400
00:22:38,860 --> 00:22:39,780
It seems that he must know about

401
00:22:39,780 --> 00:22:41,240
the situation of the mine.

402
00:22:41,620 --> 00:22:42,750
He marked this place

403
00:22:43,270 --> 00:22:44,220
by tossing the white river pebble into the well

404
00:22:44,220 --> 00:22:45,820
when he was mixing the herbs.

405
00:22:45,880 --> 00:22:46,370
Li,

406
00:22:46,700 --> 00:22:48,030
light the signal smoke.

407
00:23:28,120 --> 00:23:29,800
[Physician Xue]

408
00:23:30,350 --> 00:23:31,310
It's you.

409
00:23:32,490 --> 00:23:34,150
The physician who treated me.

410
00:23:34,300 --> 00:23:35,100
It's too late.

411
00:23:53,450 --> 00:23:54,510
What are you doing?

412
00:23:54,710 --> 00:23:55,390
Listen.

413
00:23:55,890 --> 00:23:57,490
If you dare lay a finger on me,

414
00:23:57,640 --> 00:23:59,300
my son will never forgive you.

415
00:24:09,900 --> 00:24:10,570
Li Lianhua!

416
00:24:12,140 --> 00:24:14,330
Looks like I arrived just in time.

417
00:24:14,460 --> 00:24:15,050
Be careful.

418
00:24:15,050 --> 00:24:16,570
There's poison on his palms.

419
00:24:16,570 --> 00:24:18,510
The murderer pretends to be a physician.

420
00:24:18,510 --> 00:24:19,910
You sure know how to hide.

421
00:24:34,130 --> 00:24:35,060
Why are you here?

422
00:24:35,740 --> 00:24:37,200
Let's talk about it later.

423
00:24:37,390 --> 00:24:38,190
Fang Xiaobao.

424
00:24:38,260 --> 00:24:39,090
What took you so long?

425
00:24:39,090 --> 00:24:39,570
Mother!

426
00:24:39,850 --> 00:24:41,170
Catch that bastard!

427
00:24:42,110 --> 00:24:44,460
Few people know about the emerald jade's poison.

428
00:24:44,460 --> 00:24:46,870
But you prescribed the antidote right away.

429
00:24:46,870 --> 00:24:48,200
This white river pebble

430
00:24:48,490 --> 00:24:51,220
was also a mark you threw into the dry well, right?

431
00:24:55,920 --> 00:24:57,650
The Bizhong Strike might be powerful,

432
00:24:57,650 --> 00:24:59,460
but the toxin in his body is limited.

433
00:24:59,460 --> 00:25:00,080
I'll attack the shaoyang channel,

434
00:25:00,080 --> 00:25:00,910
and you attack the queyin channel.

435
00:25:00,910 --> 00:25:02,390
This way, he can't channel the poison.

436
00:25:02,390 --> 00:25:03,660
How dare you abduct my mother?

437
00:25:03,660 --> 00:25:05,060
You're asking for death.

438
00:25:19,690 --> 00:25:20,890
Be careful, Xiaobao.

439
00:25:36,650 --> 00:25:37,310
Don't move.

440
00:25:47,590 --> 00:25:48,510
You're here too.

441
00:25:48,510 --> 00:25:49,840
After receiving your news,

442
00:25:49,840 --> 00:25:51,270
we set up a trap here

443
00:25:51,340 --> 00:25:52,200
and caught him.

444
00:25:52,220 --> 00:25:53,480
Did you see Li Lianhua?

445
00:25:54,100 --> 00:25:56,260
Didn't the two of you lock him in the post?

446
00:25:56,260 --> 00:25:57,140
He is cunning.

447
00:25:57,420 --> 00:25:58,870
He picked the lock and escaped.

448
00:25:58,870 --> 00:25:59,990
Look out for him.

449
00:26:00,270 --> 00:26:01,390
I'll bring him to justice.

450
00:26:01,390 --> 00:26:03,190
We're taking this suspect away for interrogation.

451
00:26:03,190 --> 00:26:05,190
Come to the post to find us later.

452
00:26:05,430 --> 00:26:05,760
Okay.

453
00:26:08,940 --> 00:26:09,600
Xiaobao.

454
00:26:10,910 --> 00:26:12,240
Where did Li Lianhua go?

455
00:26:13,420 --> 00:26:14,750
This guy is up to no good.

456
00:26:14,830 --> 00:26:16,630
He'd be caught if he stayed here.

457
00:26:17,530 --> 00:26:19,860
Your mother almost got poisoned just now.

458
00:26:20,210 --> 00:26:21,570
Li Lianhua saved me.

459
00:26:22,030 --> 00:26:22,900
How could you say that

460
00:26:22,900 --> 00:26:24,550
my savior is up to no good?

461
00:26:25,060 --> 00:26:25,940
How heartless.

462
00:26:27,120 --> 00:26:28,180
By the way, Mother.

463
00:26:28,740 --> 00:26:29,430
Are you okay?

464
00:26:29,430 --> 00:26:30,220
Are you hurt?

465
00:26:31,410 --> 00:26:32,620
Of course not.

466
00:26:34,220 --> 00:26:35,570
That darn physician

467
00:26:35,600 --> 00:26:37,130
caught me off guard, is all.

468
00:26:37,700 --> 00:26:39,360
But he's no better.

469
00:26:39,740 --> 00:26:42,440
He was struck by my Bone-breaking Pearl.

470
00:26:42,860 --> 00:26:44,590
He'll be suffering for a while.

471
00:26:44,600 --> 00:26:46,150
I'm glad you didn't get hurt.

472
00:26:46,150 --> 00:26:47,610
I was so worried about you.

473
00:26:47,680 --> 00:26:48,210
Alright.

474
00:26:48,460 --> 00:26:49,520
I'll take you home.

475
00:26:49,770 --> 00:26:51,300
Invite Li Lianhua over next time.

476
00:26:51,300 --> 00:26:52,660
I need to thank him properly.

477
00:26:52,660 --> 00:26:53,140
Alright.

478
00:26:53,140 --> 00:26:53,980
Got it.

479
00:26:57,960 --> 00:26:58,600
Water.

480
00:26:59,720 --> 00:27:01,560
Water. Give me water.

481
00:27:02,750 --> 00:27:03,220
Water.

482
00:27:04,310 --> 00:27:05,120
Give me water.

483
00:27:05,470 --> 00:27:07,590
Water! Water!

484
00:27:08,400 --> 00:27:09,920
There are too many toxins in his body.

485
00:27:09,920 --> 00:27:11,580
He didn't get to detoxify using Yunuqiao.

486
00:27:11,580 --> 00:27:13,730
So he desperately needs water to dilute the poison.

487
00:27:13,730 --> 00:27:14,330
Take it.

488
00:27:14,750 --> 00:27:16,750
The thing you want is in my boot.

489
00:27:18,270 --> 00:27:19,360
Give me water!

490
00:27:25,820 --> 00:27:27,300
Water! Water!

491
00:27:29,120 --> 00:27:30,700
Water.

492
00:27:31,460 --> 00:27:32,030
Water.

493
00:27:33,220 --> 00:27:34,980
Give me water.

494
00:27:36,170 --> 00:27:37,140
Water!

495
00:27:37,880 --> 00:27:39,960
Water!

496
00:27:49,380 --> 00:27:49,980
Lian Quan.

497
00:27:50,780 --> 00:27:52,710
This must be the Rama Heavenly Ice.

498
00:27:54,170 --> 00:27:56,490
I can't believe that, apart from the Jinyuan Alliance,

499
00:27:56,490 --> 00:27:59,750
even Baichuan Court knows about the Rama Heavenly Ice now.

500
00:28:00,030 --> 00:28:00,910
Not only that,

501
00:28:01,260 --> 00:28:03,150
but we also know about the searing karmic fire.

502
00:28:03,150 --> 00:28:03,980
So you'd better tell us

503
00:28:03,980 --> 00:28:06,310
about the Nanyin people's plan back then.

504
00:28:06,400 --> 00:28:08,570
Otherwise, in a few hours,

505
00:28:08,970 --> 00:28:11,630
you won't get another pail of water to detoxify with.

506
00:28:11,630 --> 00:28:12,430
I'll tell you.

507
00:28:13,350 --> 00:28:14,540
Look at me now.

508
00:28:15,170 --> 00:28:17,030
There's nothing I can't tell you.

509
00:28:17,500 --> 00:28:19,920
Back then, my ancestors and the other three individuals

510
00:28:19,920 --> 00:28:22,360
came to the Central Plains with the Rama Heavenly Ices.

511
00:28:22,360 --> 00:28:24,620
We planned to open the Rama Vessel one day

512
00:28:24,870 --> 00:28:27,600
and use it to control the millions of Midlanders.

513
00:28:28,860 --> 00:28:30,830
But the four guarding the Rama Heavenly Ices

514
00:28:30,830 --> 00:28:32,490
eventually led a wealthy life

515
00:28:32,830 --> 00:28:34,310
and didn't want to partake

516
00:28:34,690 --> 00:28:36,750
in such a dangerous venture anymore.

517
00:28:36,830 --> 00:28:38,900
I didn't expect that after all these years,

518
00:28:38,900 --> 00:28:40,700
I escaped the Jinyuan Alliance,

519
00:28:41,200 --> 00:28:42,960
but couldn't escape Baichuan Court.

520
00:28:42,960 --> 00:28:43,820
Many years ago,

521
00:28:44,200 --> 00:28:45,670
I met the Lord of the Netherworld

522
00:28:45,670 --> 00:28:46,880
once.

523
00:28:48,300 --> 00:28:50,870
Why do you look so different from him?

524
00:28:54,430 --> 00:28:56,530
I accidentally used the emerald jade to practice

525
00:28:56,530 --> 00:28:57,770
and was badly poisoned.

526
00:28:57,770 --> 00:28:59,410
My appearance had long changed.

527
00:28:59,410 --> 00:29:01,750
If I hadn't used the Sanskrit technique to change my skin,

528
00:29:01,750 --> 00:29:03,410
I wouldn't even appear human.

529
00:29:03,410 --> 00:29:05,070
A Sanskrit technique for changing your skin?

530
00:29:05,070 --> 00:29:06,470
It's a secret technique.

531
00:29:06,710 --> 00:29:08,310
Only a few enlightened monks

532
00:29:08,490 --> 00:29:11,090
can acquire the method from the Sanskrit scripts.

533
00:29:11,090 --> 00:29:12,390
It can transform a person anew

534
00:29:12,390 --> 00:29:14,190
and completely change one's appearance.

535
00:29:14,190 --> 00:29:16,320
Completely change one's appearance?

536
00:29:17,930 --> 00:29:20,780
All right, I've told you everything I know.

537
00:29:21,240 --> 00:29:23,170
You also got the Rama Heavenly Ice.

538
00:29:23,440 --> 00:29:24,370
Please let me go.

539
00:29:24,480 --> 00:29:25,410
Let you go?

540
00:29:25,850 --> 00:29:26,860
Have you ever let those girls

541
00:29:26,860 --> 00:29:28,390
who were murdered by you go?

542
00:29:29,470 --> 00:29:31,110
I'll make you pay

543
00:29:31,820 --> 00:29:34,350
for all your crimes.

544
00:29:36,060 --> 00:29:37,660
This is an important matter.

545
00:29:37,770 --> 00:29:39,620
I'm going to ask the All-Knowing Mr. Su

546
00:29:39,620 --> 00:29:41,820
to verify whether the Ice is real or not.

547
00:29:42,340 --> 00:29:44,270
I'll leave you to escort Lian Quan.

548
00:29:44,770 --> 00:29:45,630
Let’s split up.

549
00:29:47,570 --> 00:29:49,230
Since the Rama Heavenly Ice is so important,

550
00:29:49,230 --> 00:29:51,430
I can’t let you go off on your own with it.

551
00:29:51,560 --> 00:29:52,760
I should go with you.

552
00:29:54,520 --> 00:29:55,920
You still don't trust me,

553
00:29:56,840 --> 00:29:57,260
right?

554
00:29:59,040 --> 00:30:01,170
It's only right that I don't trust you.

555
00:30:01,390 --> 00:30:02,470
If we go together,

556
00:30:03,150 --> 00:30:04,650
what will happen to Lian Quan?

557
00:30:04,650 --> 00:30:06,380
Should we leave him at the post?

558
00:30:06,740 --> 00:30:07,940
Fang Duobing is here.

559
00:30:08,750 --> 00:30:09,720
It's safer to lock Lian Quan

560
00:30:09,720 --> 00:30:11,420
in the Baishui Garden bought by the Fang family

561
00:30:11,420 --> 00:30:12,790
than in the post.

562
00:30:13,920 --> 00:30:15,000
You need not worry.

563
00:30:18,020 --> 00:30:18,460
Okay.

564
00:30:19,290 --> 00:30:20,290
Come with me then.

