00:30:24,120 --> 00:30:24,780
Sister Shi.

566
00:30:25,750 --> 00:30:27,880
What are you going to do with Lian Quan?

567
00:30:28,610 --> 00:30:29,270
Three days.

568
00:30:29,500 --> 00:30:30,960
I'll be back in three days.

569
00:30:31,290 --> 00:30:33,890
I'll leave Lian Quan with you in the meanwhile.

570
00:30:35,720 --> 00:30:37,740
Alright, I'll interrogate him then.

571
00:30:37,740 --> 00:30:39,070
Interrogate Lian Quan?

572
00:30:39,090 --> 00:30:40,180
Is he hiding something?

573
00:30:40,180 --> 00:30:40,910
I think he is.

574
00:30:41,250 --> 00:30:44,180
I'll find a way to make him talk in the next three days.

575
00:30:55,470 --> 00:30:56,070
Bashi.

576
00:30:56,880 --> 00:30:57,940
You're so skilled.

577
00:30:58,430 --> 00:31:01,580
You can knead the dough in one hand and cut the dough in the other.

578
00:31:01,580 --> 00:31:03,790
My mother said

579
00:31:04,040 --> 00:31:05,370
