580
00:31:05,570 --> 00:31:07,620
they would think that the dough wasn't kneaded enough.

581
00:31:07,620 --> 00:31:09,140
But I'm strong.

582
00:31:09,420 --> 00:31:10,160
I'm used to it.

583
00:31:10,160 --> 00:31:11,560
I can't change my habit.

584
00:31:15,030 --> 00:31:16,430
Can't change your habit.

585
00:31:16,640 --> 00:31:18,200
The one who intercepted

586
00:31:18,620 --> 00:31:21,380
