587
00:31:21,380 --> 00:31:22,840
He struck with both palms.

588
00:31:23,300 --> 00:31:24,750
But the one who snuck into Baishui Garden

589
00:31:24,750 --> 00:31:26,070
had the habit of using one palm.

590
00:31:26,070 --> 00:31:27,470
There's another person.

591
00:31:28,630 --> 00:31:29,820
Who is this person?

592
00:31:29,970 --> 00:31:31,190
Two fried dough sticks.

593
00:31:31,190 --> 00:31:31,710
Okay.

594
00:31:31,850 --> 00:31:33,180
I'll put the money here.

595
00:31:37,260 --> 00:31:37,730
Bashi.

596
00:31:38,550 --> 00:31:39,870
Why did you put the money

597
00:31:39,870 --> 00:31:41,040
in a bowl of water?

598
00:31:41,170 --> 00:31:44,060
M-my hands are greasy.

599
00:31:44,080 --> 00:31:46,410
I dirty the money when I touch them.

600
00:31:48,270 --> 00:31:48,710
I see.

601
00:32:07,580 --> 00:32:08,440
Incense ashes.

602
00:32:24,830 --> 00:32:27,090
Tianji Hall's products are all the best.

603
00:32:27,620 --> 00:32:29,220
This Liushui octagonal cage

604
00:32:29,380 --> 00:32:31,580
was specially built overnight for you.

605
00:32:50,930 --> 00:32:53,710
The flowing water will help you detoxify and keep you alive.

606
00:32:53,710 --> 00:32:55,250
Very considerate, isn't it?

607
00:32:55,250 --> 00:32:55,890
But...

608
00:33:02,570 --> 00:33:04,970
If you don't tell us who your accomplice is,

609
00:33:05,020 --> 00:33:07,750
you won't be able to enjoy the life-saving water.

610
00:33:09,110 --> 00:33:10,110
What accomplice?

611
00:33:10,440 --> 00:33:11,440
Stop pretending.

612
00:33:12,020 --> 00:33:13,170
When I chased you that day,

613
00:33:13,170 --> 00:33:14,570
someone covered for you.

614
00:33:14,840 --> 00:33:16,500
Did the poison enter your brain

615
00:33:16,500 --> 00:33:17,630
and make you forget?

616
00:33:17,980 --> 00:33:19,580
That was just a thief I hired.

617
00:33:20,450 --> 00:33:21,880
Every time I abduct someone,

618
00:33:21,880 --> 00:33:24,610
I hire a thief from the underworld to act as a decoy

619
00:33:24,810 --> 00:33:26,070
so I can strike easily.

620
00:33:26,810 --> 00:33:29,330
I pay them when the deed is done

621
00:33:29,750 --> 00:33:30,840
and we never associate with each other again.

622
00:33:30,840 --> 00:33:32,450
Never associate with each other again?

623
00:33:32,450 --> 00:33:33,580
That can't be right.

624
00:33:33,880 --> 00:33:36,340
I remember my mother's Bone-breaking Pearl

625
00:33:36,380 --> 00:33:38,460
landed a solid hit on the intruder.

626
00:33:39,320 --> 00:33:41,300
The Bone-breaking Pearl strikes deep into the bones.

627
00:33:41,300 --> 00:33:42,210
But just now,

628
00:33:43,400 --> 00:33:45,330
I saw no trace of such injury on you.

629
00:33:45,810 --> 00:33:46,920
The only explanation is,

630
00:33:46,920 --> 00:33:49,220
you were not the one struck by the Bone-breaking Pearl.

631
00:33:49,220 --> 00:33:49,980
It's possible that you hired a thief

632
00:33:49,980 --> 00:33:51,610
to abduct someone for you.

633
00:33:52,190 --> 00:33:54,400
But to bear the Bone-breaking Pearl for you,

634
00:33:54,400 --> 00:33:55,930
that's not worth the price.

635
00:33:56,700 --> 00:33:57,160
Tell me.

636
00:33:57,910 --> 00:33:59,370
Where is your accomplice?

637
00:34:02,930 --> 00:34:04,260
You're quite stubborn.

638
00:34:05,460 --> 00:34:06,320
Ms. He, please.

639
00:34:12,000 --> 00:34:13,890
It's been a long time since I made a mechanism overnight.

640
00:34:13,890 --> 00:34:14,820
Because of you,

641
00:34:14,850 --> 00:34:16,090
I stayed up all night.

642
00:34:18,739 --> 00:34:20,070
These mechanical hands

643
00:34:20,230 --> 00:34:23,190
specialize in poking the most itchy and painful acupoints.

644
00:34:23,190 --> 00:34:25,420
It can change its target seven times in two hours.

645
00:34:25,420 --> 00:34:27,310
Sometimes, it'll make you cry out of pain.

646
00:34:27,310 --> 00:34:30,120
Other times, it'll make you laugh till you're breathless.

647
00:34:30,120 --> 00:34:30,920
Be sensible.

648
00:34:31,080 --> 00:34:32,290
Just answer

649
00:34:32,310 --> 00:34:33,770
whatever Xiaobao asks.

650
00:34:34,060 --> 00:34:35,870
Otherwise, prepare to suffer.

651
00:34:49,739 --> 00:34:50,219
Tell me.

652
00:34:50,699 --> 00:34:52,100
Where is the accomplice?

653
00:34:55,239 --> 00:34:57,389
Looks like you're prepared to die.

654
00:34:57,710 --> 00:34:58,590
Let me tell you.

655
00:34:58,810 --> 00:35:01,639
I haven't settled the scores with you for abducting me.

656
00:35:01,639 --> 00:35:03,570
Let's see how long you can hold out.

657
00:35:06,610 --> 00:35:07,210
By the way,

658
00:35:07,620 --> 00:35:09,550
I haven't named the mechanism yet.

659
00:35:10,660 --> 00:35:14,260
Let's call it the Lotus Acupoint Fingers.

660
00:35:15,020 --> 00:35:15,820
Fang Xiaobao.

661
00:35:15,890 --> 00:35:16,900
What do you think?

662
00:35:17,510 --> 00:35:18,970
Call me when he confesses.

663
00:35:21,300 --> 00:35:22,070
You brat.

664
00:35:22,510 --> 00:35:24,170
You're good at avoiding work.

665
00:35:30,060 --> 00:35:32,490
[Hanshui Temple]

666
00:35:41,910 --> 00:35:43,510
Master, you're so composed.

667
00:35:43,660 --> 00:35:46,190
The Bone-breaking Pearl must have hurt a lot.

668
00:35:46,820 --> 00:35:47,530
Oh, wait.

669
00:35:49,310 --> 00:35:50,910
I shouldn't call you Master.

670
00:35:51,350 --> 00:35:53,790
Should I call you Niutou,

671
00:35:54,610 --> 00:35:55,530
or Mamian?

672
00:35:56,850 --> 00:35:58,170
Didn't you see

673
00:35:58,510 --> 00:36:00,690
Niutou Manian's bodies in the mine?

674
00:36:02,120 --> 00:36:02,920
You're right.

675
00:36:03,400 --> 00:36:03,990
Yes.

676
00:36:04,380 --> 00:36:05,690
When I first saw

677
00:36:06,170 --> 00:36:07,630
the two bodies in the mine,

678
00:36:08,020 --> 00:36:10,420
I did suspect that they were Niutou Mamian.

679
00:36:11,210 --> 00:36:12,670
But out of the two corpses,

680
00:36:13,300 --> 00:36:16,310
one was heavier than the other.

681
00:36:17,020 --> 00:36:18,420
The legless body had

682
00:36:18,550 --> 00:36:20,160
a much wider pelvis bone.

683
00:36:20,480 --> 00:36:21,740
It belonged to a woman.

684
00:36:21,810 --> 00:36:24,110
So the people who died in the mine

685
00:36:24,140 --> 00:36:25,620
were not Niutou Mamian,

686
00:36:26,180 --> 00:36:27,940
but Lian Quan and his wife.

687
00:36:28,200 --> 00:36:29,200
Am I right?

688
00:36:30,020 --> 00:36:32,350
Smart people are indeed hard to deal with.

689
00:36:32,730 --> 00:36:35,170
But you're only half right.

690
00:36:36,500 --> 00:36:38,360
You killed Lian Quan and his wife,

691
00:36:38,670 --> 00:36:40,060
stole Lian Quan's secret book,

692
00:36:40,060 --> 00:36:43,310
and mastered the Bizhong Strike. But you feared being hunted by his enemies,

693
00:36:43,310 --> 00:36:44,940
so you disguised Lian Quan and his wife's bodies

694
00:36:44,940 --> 00:36:46,780
into their current state.

695
00:36:47,340 --> 00:36:47,910
Right?

696
00:36:48,510 --> 00:36:51,240
We didn't kill Lian Quan for his martial arts.

697
00:36:52,100 --> 00:36:53,830
We did it to protect ourselves.

698
00:37:09,410 --> 00:37:10,330
Many years ago,

699
00:37:10,670 --> 00:37:13,970
we were discriminated against by others for our appearance.

700
00:37:13,970 --> 00:37:15,960
But Lian Quan thought highly of us.

701
00:37:16,280 --> 00:37:17,690
We were very grateful.

702
00:37:18,010 --> 00:37:21,130
So, when the Jinyuan Alliance surrounded Lian Quan's mansion

703
00:37:21,130 --> 00:37:22,810
for the Rama Heavenly Ice,

704
00:37:23,160 --> 00:37:25,160
we risked our lives to help him escape

705
00:37:24,490 --> 00:37:26,350
[Niutou, Li Xiao]

706
00:37:24,490 --> 00:37:26,350
[Mamian, Li Xiong]

707
00:37:25,670 --> 00:37:28,070
and fled to Xiaoyuan City to live in hiding.

708
00:37:28,710 --> 00:37:29,970
But he married

709
00:37:29,990 --> 00:37:32,000
a frivolous woman here,

710
00:37:32,170 --> 00:37:33,690
and started to suspect us.

711
00:37:34,420 --> 00:37:37,030
He thought we were preying on that woman.

712
00:37:38,040 --> 00:37:40,040
Lian Quan lured us into the mine

713
00:37:40,350 --> 00:37:42,050
with the excuse of teaching us Bizhong Strike.

714
00:37:42,050 --> 00:37:43,580
Then, he made us practice on

715
00:37:43,660 --> 00:37:45,890
the poisonous emerald jade instead of emerald.

716
00:37:45,890 --> 00:37:48,690
By the time we found out, we were already poisoned.

717
00:37:49,840 --> 00:37:52,640
He thought we would die down there from the poison.

718
00:37:52,750 --> 00:37:55,610
But my younger brother, Li Xiong, reversed the skill

719
00:37:55,610 --> 00:37:58,010
and transferred all the toxins to himself.

720
00:37:58,160 --> 00:37:59,890
Then, he separated our bodies.

721
00:38:00,390 --> 00:38:01,940
Although I lost my lower limbs,

722
00:38:01,940 --> 00:38:03,000
I was not poisoned.

723
00:38:03,680 --> 00:38:05,490
I was able to move with the help of mechanisms.

724
00:38:05,490 --> 00:38:08,570
But my brother was poisoned and in critical condition.

725
00:38:08,620 --> 00:38:09,150
Brother.

726
00:38:09,870 --> 00:38:10,400
Brother!

727
00:38:10,510 --> 00:38:11,150
Don't!

728
00:38:11,290 --> 00:38:11,820
Brother!

729
00:38:13,260 --> 00:38:15,210
I was in a hurry to save my brother's life

730
00:38:15,210 --> 00:38:16,500
and tried many ways.

731
00:38:16,980 --> 00:38:19,300
Then, I finally found out that the abbot of Hanshui Temple

732
00:38:19,300 --> 00:38:22,260
owned the Yunuqiao mental codes that could detoxicate and save lives.

733
00:38:19,360 --> 00:38:24,320
[Hanshui Temple]

734
00:38:22,830 --> 00:38:26,230
I killed the abbot, stole the book, and kept my brother alive.

735
00:38:26,420 --> 00:38:27,100
After that,

736
00:38:27,270 --> 00:38:29,250
I used the identity of the abbot of Hanshui Temple

737
00:38:28,300 --> 00:38:29,960
[Hanshui Temple]

738
00:38:29,490 --> 00:38:30,950
to remain in Xiaoyuan City

739
00:38:30,960 --> 00:38:32,740
-and take revenge on Lian Quan.
-Brother.

740
00:38:32,740 --> 00:38:33,070
Look.

741
00:38:33,820 --> 00:38:34,430
I found it.

742
00:38:35,920 --> 00:38:37,960
[Yunuqiao Mental Codes]

743
00:38:40,240 --> 00:38:40,760
Madam.

744
00:38:41,090 --> 00:38:42,020
At last, one day,

745
00:38:42,910 --> 00:38:45,110
I managed to lure Lian Quan into the mine

746
00:38:45,590 --> 00:38:47,250
and killed him and that woman.

747
00:38:47,700 --> 00:38:48,570
Then, I disguised the bodies

748
00:38:48,570 --> 00:38:50,130
to look like us.

749
00:38:51,000 --> 00:38:53,790
This way, even if the Jinyuan Alliance finds out,

750
00:38:54,860 --> 00:38:56,630
they won't suspect us.

751
00:39:03,580 --> 00:39:05,460
Everything was perfect.

752
00:39:05,980 --> 00:39:07,970
But while we avoided the Jinyuan Alliance,

753
00:39:07,970 --> 00:39:09,500
we couldn't avoid you guys.

754
00:39:09,680 --> 00:39:10,790
My brother, Lee Xiong,

755
00:39:10,790 --> 00:39:12,250
has been captured, right?

756
00:39:13,060 --> 00:39:14,630
He's in the hands of the Baichuan Court.

757
00:39:14,630 --> 00:39:16,830
Fortunately, I'm not that unlucky.

758
00:39:17,500 --> 00:39:19,320
God gave me

759
00:39:19,340 --> 00:39:20,580
a chance to survive.

760
00:39:20,960 --> 00:39:22,760
Your identity has been exposed.

761
00:39:22,970 --> 00:39:24,430
You still want to survive?

762
00:39:24,620 --> 00:39:26,890
With Li Xiangyi, the leader of the Sigu Sect here,

763
00:39:26,890 --> 00:39:27,920
of course I can.

764
00:39:28,740 --> 00:39:31,520
That day, you used Whirling Steps when you were chasing me.

765
00:39:31,520 --> 00:39:32,380
Sect Leader Li,

766
00:39:32,650 --> 00:39:33,820
you can't fool me.

767
00:39:34,190 --> 00:39:35,520
If it were Lee Xiangyi,

768
00:39:37,110 --> 00:39:39,110
do you think you could have escaped?

769
00:39:41,660 --> 00:39:42,520
Sect Leader Li,

770
00:39:42,830 --> 00:39:44,910
you came all the way to Xiaoyan City.

771
00:39:45,340 --> 00:39:47,190
Surely, your goal is the Rama Heavenly Ice,

772
00:39:47,190 --> 00:39:48,990
just like the Jinyuan Alliance.

773
00:39:49,020 --> 00:39:50,480
Promise me one condition,

774
00:39:50,800 --> 00:39:53,460
and I'll happily give you the Rama Heavenly Ice.

775
00:39:53,510 --> 00:39:55,860
The Baichuan Court has already acquired it

776
00:39:55,860 --> 00:39:56,920
from your brother.

777
00:39:58,380 --> 00:40:00,430
That one is naturally a fake.

778
00:40:00,960 --> 00:40:02,840
We have no one to depend on.

779
00:40:03,310 --> 00:40:05,220
The Rama Heavenly Ice is our lifesaver.

780
00:40:05,220 --> 00:40:06,880
I have to keep it until the end.

781
00:40:07,060 --> 00:40:09,070
But now I have you, Li Xiangyi.

782
00:40:09,380 --> 00:40:10,770
I can give the Ice away.

783
00:40:11,340 --> 00:40:12,200
Sect Leader Li.

784
00:40:12,410 --> 00:40:13,070
Promise me,

785
00:40:13,260 --> 00:40:14,880
and the Rama Heavenly Ice is yours.

786
00:40:14,880 --> 00:40:17,260
Otherwise, I'll hand it over to the Jinyuan Alliance.

787
00:40:17,260 --> 00:40:19,180
Although they are not as trustworthy as you,

788
00:40:19,180 --> 00:40:21,580
they're still capable of keeping us alive.

789
00:40:22,420 --> 00:40:23,020
Tell me.

790
00:40:23,780 --> 00:40:25,110
What do you want me to do?

791
00:40:26,630 --> 00:40:27,960
Save my brother Li Xiong

792
00:40:28,210 --> 00:40:30,210
and cure his Bizhong Strike poison.

793
00:40:30,510 --> 00:40:31,120
I know.

794
00:40:31,830 --> 00:40:34,760
The Yangzhouman is the best inner power in the world.

795
00:40:34,930 --> 00:40:36,660
Only you can cure him.

796
00:40:37,250 --> 00:40:37,940
Li Xiao.

797
00:40:38,500 --> 00:40:39,830
You're too optimistic.

798
00:40:40,460 --> 00:40:42,810
I'm no longer a member of the Baichuan Court.

799
00:40:42,810 --> 00:40:45,290
I'm wanted on the Blade List.

800
00:40:45,550 --> 00:40:47,430
I can't save your brother.

801
00:40:47,900 --> 00:40:49,540
That's your problem now.

802
00:40:49,820 --> 00:40:51,350
It has nothing to do with me.

803
00:40:51,460 --> 00:40:54,390
I know you're close to Fang Duobing,

804
00:40:54,420 --> 00:40:56,280
the detective of Baichuan Court.

805
00:40:56,720 --> 00:40:58,720
You might be able to use him for this.

806
00:40:59,370 --> 00:40:59,890
Finally,

807
00:40:59,890 --> 00:41:01,670
Sect Leader Li, let me remind you.

808
00:41:01,670 --> 00:41:02,930
You only have two days.

809
00:41:02,990 --> 00:41:03,860
Once the time is up,

810
00:41:03,860 --> 00:41:06,060
I'll ask the Jinyuan Alliance for help.

811
00:41:06,600 --> 00:41:07,730
You better hurry up.

812
00:41:09,230 --> 00:41:11,620
Looks like I'll have to offend Fang Xiaobao again.

813
00:41:11,620 --> 00:41:13,480
It's not a big deal to promise you.

814
00:41:13,530 --> 00:41:15,750
But I'm worried.

815
00:41:17,310 --> 00:41:18,170
Sect Leader Li.

816
00:41:18,820 --> 00:41:20,160
What are you worried about?

817
00:41:20,160 --> 00:41:21,710
Your brother's Ice is fake.

818
00:41:22,220 --> 00:41:24,700
I have to check if your Ice

819
00:41:24,850 --> 00:41:25,850
is real.

820
00:41:33,290 --> 00:41:34,950
Li Xiangyi is a man of his word.

821
00:41:35,300 --> 00:41:37,560
I believe you won’t take the treasure by force.

822
00:41:37,560 --> 00:41:40,160
You don't have to threaten me with my past reputation.

823
00:41:40,160 --> 00:41:41,420
I'm only confirming its authenticity.

824
00:41:41,420 --> 00:41:42,880
I won't snatch it from you.

825
00:42:00,310 --> 00:42:00,850
Deal.

826
00:42:03,360 --> 00:42:04,160
Fang Xiaobao.

827
00:42:04,740 --> 00:42:06,270
Why did you lock the prison?

828
00:42:06,830 --> 00:42:08,890
The physician hasn't confessed yet.

829
00:42:10,100 --> 00:42:10,740
Your mechanism poked him

830
00:42:10,740 --> 00:42:12,790
till he was frothing in the mouth, yet he was silent.

831
00:42:12,790 --> 00:42:14,850
It means he won't tell on his partner.

832
00:42:14,980 --> 00:42:16,440
It's useless to force him.

833
00:42:17,430 --> 00:42:20,290
Even the mechanism made by me, the Tianji Hall Sect Master,

834
00:42:20,290 --> 00:42:21,490
can't get him to fess up?

835
00:42:21,490 --> 00:42:22,860
I refuse to admit defeat.

836
00:42:22,860 --> 00:42:23,300
Go.

837
00:42:23,350 --> 00:42:24,480
Open the door.

